{"tid":2437801,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"響應國際婦女節　Rosé 送上兩大驚喜！","createTime":"2021-03-08T06:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T14:12:34.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"15202dc29285ed17f8ce252309d927ac895c56ad","tid":2437801,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_d402d6db4ee8158b56676e72aa146715/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-08/134109-899230.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_d402d6db4ee8158b56676e72aa146715%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-08%2F134109-899230.png&h=3dc80a4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在國際婦女節這天，BLACKPINK 的 Ros&eacute; 除了釋出新歌 MV 預告片外，還親自推薦了一份播放清單！<br />\n<br />\nYG Entertainment 今天（8 日）公開了 Ros&eacute; 首張個人單曲〈R〉主打歌 &ldquo;On the Ground&rdquo; 的 MV 預告片，以一段坐著車穿過燦爛夜燈，彷彿電影般的影像襯托旋律，透過 Ros&eacute; 的肢體動作，呈現出由華麗的工作狀態轉換成個人時間的過渡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_W8y2A9sK6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_W8y2A9sK6s&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058gWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=329892ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_W8y2A9sK6s</a><br />\n<br />\n這支影片是 Ros&eacute; 繼一個月前的 &ldquo;COMING SOON&rdquo; 後再度釋出了預告片，公開約半天就已吸引近 500 萬人次觀看，可見大家都等不及迎來 Ros&eacute; 的個人作品。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，Ros&eacute; 今天也參與了 Apple Music 的特別活動，配合「女性遠見卓識者」(Visionary Women) 主題推薦了 25 首歌組成的播放清單，除了 BLACKPINK 自己的 &ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo;、&ldquo;Lovesick Girls&rdquo;、Jennie 的 &ldquo;SOLO&rdquo; 外，還有 Amy Winehouse 的 &ldquo;Lose is a losing game&rdquo; 等。特別的是，Ros&eacute; 是本次唯一獲邀參加本活動的韓國歌手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_78938ce17f509595370f64e7e808d33c/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-08/134109-899231.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_78938ce17f509595370f64e7e808d33c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-08%2F134109-899231.jpeg&h=c44ac8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment、roses_are_rosie）"},{"pid":"4b9564077aaa662ec99f1c0ab80138f12107eba4","tid":2437801,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:00:48.000Z","msg":"很正..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a35d0187123875c9110ea632d69faa48cf33a2","tid":2437801,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:00:59.000Z","msg":"臭38 除衫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518757f21e52343b1827b57598e4b3315d8c021f","tid":2437801,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"勁支持...！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb8b6ad45c100b7b908330bb41c3c4d2e53f9dc","tid":2437801,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"👀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27361b552a79297fd3239cd527711c3d3429d4c","tid":2437801,"uid":384468,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"乜都唔做 坐定定喺度都可以撞飛t寶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15973147fd8958e7647136149ce6da6e503efcb7","tid":2437801,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a35d0187123875c9110ea632d69faa48cf33a2","tid":2437801,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:00:59.000Z","msg":"臭38 除衫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"你係咪精蟲上腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9734f47f95af8028e4599f3ba10461589a6863f3","tid":2437801,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d27361b552a79297fd3239cd527711c3d3429d4c","tid":2437801,"uid":384468,"like":5,"dislik